data.description: REDUCED!  Inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, perfect for first-time buyers! Embrace the open floorplan, complete with a spacious eat-in kitchen, breakfast bar, and a light-filled living room. Essential appliances—refrigerator, washer, and dryer—are included. The master suite boasts a walk-in closet and a stylish new subway-tiled shower. Recent upgrades by the owners feature a new hot water heater, ceiling fans in bedrooms, a modern dining room light fixture, and fresh blinds throughout. Discover the large backyard, a blank canvas for your personalized oasis, complemented by a new sprinkler system for added convenience. This community, spanning over 400 acres, offers parks, picnic areas, a stocked lake with a fishing pier, hike and bike trails, swimming pools, sports fields, and a fitness center. Your journey as a homeowner begins here!
